notes: Land seizure: On 1 November 2024, Israeli settlers set up a tent on a Palestinian-owned land in Shi'b Al Batim (Hebron, West Bank).

On 1 November 2024, protesters held a large Houthi-sponsored protest in Dawran Aness district (coded to district center Dawran ad Daydah) (Dhamar) in solidarity with the Palestinian and Lebanese people and with Houthi actions against the 'Zionist enemy' in the context of the latest round of violence in Israel-Palestine.
